ActPatent Act
SubjectRules Amending the Patent Rules
PrecisRules Amending the PATENT RULES in order to harmonize the qualifying examination process and eligibility criteria to sit for the qualifying examinations in order to help ensure that agents entered on the Register of Patent Agents and the List of Trade-mark Agents have a comprehensive knowledge of Intellectual Property law before entering into practice. Harmonization of the eligibility criteria to simplify the processes for those individuals who work as both patent and trade-mark agents.
